    Operator -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS<br/>SA token<br/>CRD watch + SSA"| K8sAPI
    MLflow -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS<br/>Client SA token<br/>SubjectAccessReview"| K8sAPI
    MLflow -->|"TCP/5432 or 3306<br/>TLS optional<br/>URI credentials"| DB
    MLflow -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS<br/>Cloud credentials"| ArtifactStore

    %% Monitoring
    Prometheus -->|"HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS (service-ca)<br/>Bearer Token"| MetricsEP

    %% service-ca
    ServiceCA -.->|"provisions certs"| MLflowAPI
    ServiceCA -.->|"provisions certs"| MetricsEP

